package: Java.util.Sacanner;

Java OOPS:

1. class & Object
2. Abstraction
3. Encapsulation
4. Polymorphism
5. Inheritance

Constructor
*Class name and function name same
*function wil be invoke automatically while object creating of class
\*Types:Default,Parameteriesd and private constructor

Final Keyword

- Prevent override method
- prevent extend class
- prevent modify variable value

Abstract class

- cannot create obejct for abstract class
- Always abstract class should be inherited
- using subclass object can access abstract class methods
- it wil have abstract and non-abstract method
- abstract method should be implemented in sub class

Exception Handling:

- Try block - actual logic should go
- Catch block - Exception handled by in runtime
- finally block - Always excuted

Syntax:
try{
//codes
}
catch(Exception ex){
//codes
}
finally{

}

1. Compilation Errors
2. Runtime Errors
